This is to show how to use the promises.
What promises are and how they behave
Please refer the below link for more details: http://blog.mediumequalsmessage.com/promise-deferred-objects-in-javascript-pt2-practical-use


Steps to use this repository:

1. clone this to your desktop
2. cd into this directory
3. run> bower install
4. open the index.html

Go though the console and understand the flow. Used the setTimeOut() to add some delay for each promises.